{"tid":547830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得Xhaka 俾人低估得好緊要","createTime":"2018-02-02T01:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T10:30:44.000Z","uid":44584,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd238c81c51e91a467c6173b65493c46d6f0ec1","tid":547830,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"Xhaka賣點絕對係頭腦 <br />\n佢嘅地波長傳(forward pass)經常可以直接搵到隊友 穿越對方中場線 視野(vision)同準繩度兼備 連接後場同前場<br />\n其次 佢防守上嘅企位(positioning)經常出現喺最適合嘅位置 路斯基曾經講過 同佢中場拍檔好舒服 因為Xhaka總會出現喺適當位置 補番佢嘅位<br />\n雲加曾經講過 Xhaka有能力為巴塞隆拿效力<br />\n基奧特喺佢嘅告別賽講過 佢喺英格蘭(England)球壇得到嘅讚美同賞識實在太少(too lees)<br />\n摩連奴多次讚美Xhaka 話如果可以買到就好 仲讚美佢係一個好聰明(handsome)嘅球員<br />\n少入國家隊唔係佢問題 係瑞士On9 <br />\n佢係頂級嘅墜後型playmaker 我個人認為佢可以同迪羅斯 布斯基斯相比<br />\n踢過/睇過波就知 能夠轉守為攻 真係好重要(very important)<br />\n順便講埋 佢好似係2017年阿仙奴年度最佳球員 <br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 非阿仙奴球迷 只不過係Xhaka嘅球迷"},{"pid":"157b94b92bc69b529a1ef9943b359f594a17a410","tid":547830,"uid":235,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7d62f2fbdadff549da456259100f142861327ba","tid":547830,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"同意(Agree)"},{"pid":"d2f6d8ae450383915159a580e39a65b610e7933d","tid":547830,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"3cbb685575db0a1c5ddd24d9103e403f42d80b25","tid":547830,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fcd238c81c51e91a467c6173b65493c46d6f0ec1","tid":547830,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"Xhaka賣點絕對係頭腦 <br />\n佢嘅地波長傳(forward pass)經常可以直接搵到隊友 穿越對方中場線 視野(vision)同準繩度兼備 連接後場同前場<br />\n其次 佢防守上嘅企位(positioning)經常出現喺最適合嘅位置 路斯基曾經講過 同佢中場拍檔好舒服 因為Xhaka總會出現喺適當位置 補番佢嘅位<br />\n雲加曾經講過 Xhaka有能力為巴塞隆拿效力<br />\n基奧特喺佢嘅告別賽講過 佢喺英格蘭(England)球壇得到嘅讚美同賞識實在太少(too lees)<br />\n摩連奴多次讚美Xhaka 話如果可以買到就好 仲讚美佢係一個好聰明(handsome)嘅球員<br />\n少入國家隊唔係佢問題 係瑞士On9 <br />\n佢係頂級嘅墜後型playmaker 我個人認為佢可以同迪羅斯 布斯基斯相比<br />\n踢過/睇過波就知 能夠轉守為攻 真係好重要(very important)<br />\n順便講埋 佢好似係2017年阿仙奴年度最佳球員 <br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 非阿仙奴球迷 只不過係Xhaka嘅球迷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:20:43.000Z","msg":"可能我真心左。<br />\nhandsome 解聰明?"},{"pid":"1895628abd2e966bc0a13610c8ded33ef74c0d4c","tid":547830,"uid":149073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"英文就冇人捉錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee96049318f674669e611f5db091aef85fa4a5ed","tid":547830,"uid":21896,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"戇鳩（on9)"},{"pid":"add11f4354ca8aa0b554c9f98316db918c35d68f","tid":547830,"uid":33506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee96049318f674669e611f5db091aef85fa4a5ed","tid":547830,"uid":21896,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"戇鳩（on9)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166f2f48092618b9d108fbcb511eb5a72562cad2","tid":547830,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add11f4354ca8aa0b554c9f98316db918c35d68f","tid":547830,"uid":33506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee96049318f674669e611f5db091aef85fa4a5ed","tid":547830,"uid":21896,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"戇鳩（on9)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1fd4e69cf7591be9787f9b24ea27dc2d0c33c0","tid":547830,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"路斯基同佢中揚拍檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d45927040354352667ee2ae85f1f3d78d666a80","tid":547830,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Xhaka賣點絕對係頭腦 <br />\n佢嘅地波長傳(forward pass)經常可以直接搵到隊友 穿越對方中場線 視野(vision)同準繩度兼備 連接後場同前場<span style=\"color: red;\"> (okay 但有時唔太穩定)</span><br />\n其次 佢防守上嘅企位(positioning)經常出現喺最適合嘅位置 路斯基曾經講過 同佢中場拍檔好舒服 因為Xhaka總會出現喺適當位置 補番佢嘅位 <span style=\"color: red;\">(唔同意，反而覺得佢防守意識差，唔識mark人補位，尤其係畀人打反擊)</span><br />\n雲加曾經講過 Xhaka有能力為巴塞隆拿效力 <span style=\"color: red;\">(一定唔夠班)</span><br />\n基奧特喺佢嘅告別賽講過 佢喺英格蘭(England)球壇得到嘅讚美同賞識實在太少(too lees)<br />\n摩連奴多次讚美Xhaka 話如果可以買到就好 仲讚美佢係一個好聰明(handsome)嘅球員 <br />\n少入國家隊唔係佢問題 係瑞士On9 <br />\n佢係頂級嘅墜後型playmaker 我個人認為佢可以同迪羅斯 布斯基斯相比 <br />\n踢過/睇過波就知 能夠轉守為攻 真係好重要(very important)<br />\n順便講埋 佢好似係2017年阿仙奴年度最佳球員 <br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 非阿仙奴球迷 只不過係Xhaka嘅球迷</blockquote>"},{"pid":"046f4e74cc2337bbec963b2e4c9c71286e72e0e7","tid":547830,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"雲加(God)"},{"pid":"ddfb04d28776d217b2d4219d3d664df737a07e3d","tid":547830,"uid":37976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"啲英文咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英格蘭都要England<br />\nHandsome變左聰明"},{"pid":"68f11108b41dcf02880fdf9b16c99a5303d03e2b","tid":547830,"uid":58863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re